    <item>
      <title>企业贷款机构正在锁定保护措施，以防高利率陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/corporate-lenders-are-seeking-protection-against-tough-times-from-high-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高风险、负债累累的公司的放贷者日益要求获得保护，避免在困难时期采取削弱债权人的融资手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/corporate-lenders-are-seeking-protection-against-tough-times-from-high-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:37:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>锂资源匮乏，巴斯夫取消智利投资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/basf-pulls-plug-on-potential-chile-investments-amid-lithium-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球电动汽车普及率放缓导致电池金属价格下跌，德国化工巨头巴斯夫公司放弃了投资智利锂矿资产的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/basf-pulls-plug-on-potential-chile-investments-amid-lithium-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:31:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国北约大使谈援助乌克兰、结束战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-02/us-nato-ambassador-on-aid-for-ukraine-ending-the-war-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻北约大使朱丽安·史密斯表示，她谈到在乌克兰与俄罗斯交战期间继续向其提供货币和军事援助。她还谈到了盟国如何合作以及中国在冲突中的作用。她接受了彭博社的克里蒂·古普塔的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-02/us-nato-ambassador-on-aid-for-ukraine-ending-the-war-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:24:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
