      <title>智利利用 17 亿美元社会债券开拓全球债务市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/chile-taps-debt-markets-with-7-year-social-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利通过发行社会债券进入债务市场，这是新兴市场主权国家在 2024 年初的一系列活动之后，预计下半年将有所放缓的首批债券之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/chile-taps-debt-markets-with-7-year-social-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场在鲍威尔的通货紧缩观点下获得喘息机会：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在杰罗姆·鲍威尔 (Jerome Powell) 指出美国已重回通货紧缩轨道后，债券市场停止了近期的抛售，交易员开始关注美联储降息的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 22:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
